flowchart TD
    A([User]) -->|arrives via| B{Acquisition channel}
    B -->|Instagram / TikTok| C[Social / Paid Ad]
    B -->|Affiliate link| D[Affiliate Partner]
    B -->|QR code| E[Physical / Event]
    B -->|Web / AI search| F[SEO / ChatGPT / Claude]
    C & D & E & F --> G[Shopify website\nProducts · Cart · Stock · Tracking]
    G --> H{Engages RAG assistant?}
    H -->|Yes| I[RAG assistant\nStyle advice · Questionnaire · Virtual try-on]
    H -->|No| J
    I --> J[Purchase]
    J --> K[Back-office\nScan product · Register customer · Assign code]
    K --> L[Shipping\nCarrier label · Tracking]
    L --> M[Customer registry\nConfirmation + tracking email]
    M --> N{Post-sale}
    N -->|Marketing| O[Personalised advice\nNew arrivals · Loyalty programme]
    N -->|Analytics| P[(Data Platform\nOrders · RAG logs · Marketing events)]
    P --> Q[Dashboard\nRevenue · Forecast · Stock alerts]
    P --> R[ML Forecasting\nStock & demand planning]
    Q & R --> S[Operations team\nStock decisions · Campaign planning]
